blog.title: 8 DAYS OF ONE DIRECTION
blog.description: 8 DAYS OF ONE DIRECTION is a project, solely dedicated to One Direction and it's Directioners. We're trying to get Directioners to come as one by showcasing Their talent and creating and sharing Their Work.

summary: 8 DAYS OF ONE DIRECTION Hey, everyone! We were inspired by 5 DAYS OF LOUIS and we're very happy to announce 8 DAYS OF ONE...
body:
8 DAYS OF ONE DIRECTION

Hey, everyone!

We were inspired by 5 DAYS OF LOUIS and we’re very happy to announce 8 DAYS OF ONE DIRECTION- A project we’re arranging as a way to celebrate One Direction’s 8th Anniversary.

Beginning on 16 July 2018 and ending on 23 July 2018. Each day, you, as a Directioner, will be able to create Edits, Graphics, Fan-Art, Manips and Moodboards, as well as Audios and Videos, based on These Topics:-

  1. 16 July 2018 | One Direction+Favourite Album
  2. 17 July 2018 | One Direction+Favourite Music Video
  3. 18 July 2018 | One Direction+Favourite Song
  4. 19 July 2018 | One Direction+Favourite Interview Moments
  5. 20 July 2018 | One Direction+Favourite Tour Moments
  6. 21 July 2018 | One Direction+Favourite OT5/OT4 Moments
  7. 22 July 2018 | One Direction+Favourite Bromance
  8. 23 July 2018 | One Direction+8th Anniversary

Whenever you post your Work, be sure to Tag it with #8DO1D and Tag us as well, so, we can see your Work! 

Also, we’ll be having daily WMYB STREAMING PARTIES, in order to get The WMYB Music Video to 1B. 

  • AUSTRALIA | 3:00 A.M. (03:00)
  • BRAZIL | 1:00 P.M. (13:00)
  • CANADA | 12:00 P.M. (12:00)
  • CHINA | 12:00 A.M. (0:00)
  • FRANCE | 5:00 P.M. (17:00)
  • GERMANY | 5:00 P.M. (17:00)
  • INDIA | 9:30 P.M. (21:30)
  • INDONESIA | 11:00 P.M. (23:00)
  • ITALY | 5:00 P.M. (17:00)
  • JAPAN | 1:00 A.M. (1:00)
  • MEXICO | 10:00 A.M. (10:00)
  • PAKISTAN | 9:00 P.M. (21:00)
  • RUSSIA | 7:00 P.M. (19:00)
  • SAUDI ARABIA | 7:00 P.M. (19:00)
  • SOUTH AFRICA | 6:00 P.M. (18:00)
  • SOUTH KOREA | 1:00 A.M. (1:00)
  • TURKEY | 7:00 P.M. (19:00)
  • UNITED KINGDOM | 4:00 P.M. (16:00)
  • UNITED STATES | 12:00 A.M. (12:00)    

Would you like to co-lead The 8 DAYS OF ONE DIRECTION Project with us? Direct-Message us. Any questions, suggestions and regards are welcome in The Ask Box! :-) 

Follow us to be able to get any Updates, which we may we post. 

We certainly hope you can join us during our WMYB STREAMING PARTIES, as well as contribute in our 8 DAYS OF ONE DIRECTION Project!

tags: harry styles live on tour sacramento
even this was anxiety inducing for me
body:
9 July 2018, Harry Styles in Sacramento

So I just saw harry last night for the first time since his new tour began and I just am at a loss for words. It was the first show that I went to alone in the sense that I traveled for it by myself since I became legal and it was just a wild experience for me. I am so grateful that I have the opportunity to do this and have such a wonderful reason as to why. I am so lucky to have parents that allow me to do this and I am so thankful for that but I also have to give a honor the reason why I did this, Harry Styles. If not for him and his music that means more to me than I can ever properly explain, I would not have even considered this trip which has not only been an excuse for me to travel but an experience that has given me self confidence as I have proved to not only myself but also my parents how capable I am. I believe in myself more than ever and it has been a type of exposure therapy in the sense that I had to do it on my own and although it was something I wanted to do my anxiety is usually an issue with doing things I enjoy or trying things I know I will like. Overall this is just a sappy letter to prove why it is important for people to support their loved ones and that concerts are about more than just the music, also for me to write out what I feel but would never tell anyone irl. Thank you for this Harry.
